Nijimori Studio was such a beautiful place to visit! I've always wanted to go to Japan but haven't had the chance, so I've wanted to go to Nijimori Studio for a long time! Unfortunately, the weather was very hot the day I visited ã… ã…  I'll definitely go again when it's not so scorching! Renting the kimonos was pretty easy, and there were a lot of options to choose from. They had all sorts of extra things you could choose like shoes or hair accessories or a bag.
